  "description": {
   "en": "Hailing from a country of grasslands, Saraana married into the great nation of Kouyoku for peace. Inside the palace, there was the beautiful emperor and his queen, who bared an equally beautiful hostility. She is thrown into a world of conspiracy, schemes, and secrets. Using her inherit determination and wit, she cuts through her cruel fate and deepens her bond with the emperor Shuurei (Zhu Li). However, there is somene targeting the two of them...? From a skillful author comes the dramatic tale of a spectacular Chinese romance!",
   "ja": "胸が熱くなる!ドラマチック後宮ロマン\n\n草原の国から和平のため、大国・煌燿国の後宮に嫁いだサラーナ。\nそこには麗しき皇帝と、美しく敵意むき出しの后たちがいた。\n\n渦巻く陰謀と策略、そして秘密。\n過酷な運命を持ち前の勝ち気さと機転で切り抜けていくサラーナは次第に\n皇帝・朱麗との絆を深めるが、2人を狙う者が・・・!?\n\n実力派作家が描く、\nドラマチック中華スペクタクルロマン!"
  },
